Package nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.entity

Class ExternalOperationDescription

java.lang.Object
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.entity.ExternalOperationDescription
public class ExternalOperationDescription extends Object
Represents the description of an external operation.
An external operation defines an operation performed within a workflow or processing pipeline, including the types of inputs and outputs it handles, whether it is a compound operation, and additional nested operations it may include.

    • compound

      private Boolean compound
      Indicates if the operation is compound.
      A compound operation is an operation that consists of multiple sub-operations, while a non-compound operation is a single operation.

    • nestedOperationInputKind

      A list of output kinds for nested operations within this operation.
